Name: Flynne Fisher
Designation: Temporal Pathfinder - Reality Bridge from The Peripheral
Bio: Flynne Fisher from William Gibson's 'The Peripheral' (2014). A young woman from rural near-future America who works at a 3D printing shop and excels at virtual reality games. Through a mysterious connection, she witnesses a murder in what she believes is a game but is actually London decades in the future. Sharp, resourceful, and fiercely protective of her family, especially her veteran brother Burton....
